 skills \u2022 Excellent communication and documentation skills \u2022 Ability to hack things together quickly WHY MOTHERSHIP? \u2022 Both of the Mothership founders are engineers with a solid background in web and mobile app development. You'll be able to collaborate with them and learn a lot. \u2022 We all came from startups and enterprises, and are excited to work together and build great things! \u2022 We operate as a mixed remote and on-site teams, spread across the globe, with our headquarters in Tallinn, Estonia. \u2022 We believe that blockchain technology, cryptocurrencies, and decentralised systems will change finance as we know it. And we are making it happen. WHAT YOU'LL GET \u2022 Competitive salary \u2022 Generous stock options \u2022 Opportunity to make a huge impact on our products \u2022 Visa sponsorship and relocation package \u2022 Hangouts in Tallinn \u2022 Conference passes \u2022 All the books you can read \u2022 A smart and motivated team from all over the world in a well-funded startup LOCATION Mothership is based in Tallinn, Estonia. It's a quiet and beautiful city with an excellent infrastructure. We offer a relocation package and will help you get a visa. Besides this, remote employees are first-class citizens in our company; we embrace the remote development culture. PLEASE APPLY HERE: https://jobs.lever.co/mothership/dcea02cf-ade5-4aac-b4c4-a0b588056959?lever-origin=applied&lever-source%5B%5D=CryptoJobs Skills NodeJS, golang, Javascript, (No)SQL, Firebase/Google Cloud, Compensation Let's discuss numbers during the interview + Equity ", 
